<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fy kl ywm ạ̉lms dwmaⁿạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fy kl ywm ạ̉lms .. dwmaⁿạ rby jmạlaⁿạ lsẖkẖṣk
 (ạ̉lms ḥbaⁿạ ybhj qlby .. ạ̉lms ṣdqaⁿạ bwʿdk)2
 ạlqrạr- frḥẗ qlby fyk ạ̹lhy .. gẖdy wywmy tbqy̱ ạ̉myn
 kmạ bạ̉ms knt ạ̉mynaⁿạ .. tbqy̱ ạ̉mynaⁿạ fy kl ḥyn
 2- fy kl ḍyqy wʿdk rby .. lst wḥydaⁿạ fy krbk
 (ʿny tzyl kl ṣʿạb .. yʿlw htạfy bsẖkrk)2
 3- fy kl ḍʿfy tsnd nfsy .. yhms dwmaⁿạ ly ṣwtk
 (ạ̹ny ạjtzt qblk ywmaⁿạ .. nʿmty tkfy fy ḍʿfk)2</lyrics>
<author>hạny mnybr ḥbyb, sạmḥ rwbyl</author>
<hymn_number>333</hymn_number>
</song>